author: Epiphanius, Saint, Bishop of Constantia in Cyprus, ca. 310-403
title: Tou agiou patros emon Epiphaniou ... Peri ton physiologon. Tou autou Eis ta baia logos. Sancti patris nostri Epiphanii ... Ad physiologum. Eiusdem In die festo palmarum sermo. D. Consali Ponce de Leon Hispalensis ... interpretis & scholiaste, bimestre oti
